#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:18
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Controlling resource usage can be very effective when trying to prevent a local\n"
"Denial of Service or restricting the maximum allowed logins for a group or user.\n"
"However, too strict settings will impede on your system's behavior and will\n"
"result in program failures so make sure that you check each setting first.\n"
msgstr ""
"リソースを制御する手法はローカルからのDOS攻撃を防ぐ場合や、グループやユーザで許可される最大同時ログイン数を制限する場合に効果的です。\n"
"しかし、厳しすぎる設定はシステムの動作の妨げになり、結果としてプログラムの実行が失敗するため、最初にそれぞれの設定をチェックしてください。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:25
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*    soft core 0\n"
"*    hard core 0\n"
"*    hard nproc 15\n"
"*    hard rss 10000\n"
"*    -    maxlogins 2\n"
"@dev hard core 100000\n"
"@dev soft nproc 20\n"
"@dev hard nproc 35\n"
"@dev -    maxlogins 10\n"
msgstr ""
"*    soft core 0\n"
"*    hard core 0\n"
"*    hard nproc 15\n"
"*    hard rss 10000\n"
"*    -    maxlogins 2\n"
"@dev hard core 100000\n"
"@dev soft nproc 20\n"
"@dev hard nproc 35\n"
"@dev -    maxlogins 10\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:37
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you find yourself trying to set <c>nproc</c> or <c>maxlogins</c> to 0, maybe\n"
"you should delete the user instead. The example above sets the group <c>dev</c>\n"
"settings for processes, core file and <c>maxlogins</c>. The rest is set to a\n"
"default value.\n"
msgstr ""
"<c>nproc</c>や<c>maxlogins</c>を0に設定するなら、その代わりにユーザを削除した方が良いでしょう。\n"
"上記の例では<c>dev</c>グループのプロセス、coreファイルと<c>maxlogins</c>の設定を行っています。\n"
"残りの部分はデフォルト値です。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><note>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:44
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<path>/etc/security/limits.conf</path> is part of the PAM package and will\n"
"only apply to packages that use PAM.\n"
msgstr "<path>/etc/security/limits.conf</path>はPAMパッケージの一部で、PAMを使うパッケージにのみ適用されます。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:51 en/security/shb-limits.xml:61
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/limits"
msgstr "/etc/limits"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:55
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<path>/etc/limits</path> is very similar to the limit file\n"
"<path>/etc/security/limits.conf</path>. The only difference is the format and\n"
"that it only works on users or wild cards (not groups). Let's have a look at a\n"
"sample configuration:\n"
msgstr ""
"<path>/etc/limits</path>は制限を行うファイル<path>/etc/security/limits.conf</path>と大変似ています。\n"
"ただ一つの違いはフォーマットで、この制限はユーザもしくはワイルドカードでの指定でしか機能しません(グループで指定できません)。\n"
"サンプルの設定を見てみましょう。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:62
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*   L2 C0 U15 R10000\n"
"kn L10 C100000 U35\n"
msgstr ""
"*   L2 C0 U15 R10000\n"
"kn L10 C100000 U35\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:67
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Here we set the default settings and a specific setting for the user kn.  Limits\n"
"are part of the sys-apps/shadow package. It is not necessary to set any limits\n"
"in this file if you have enabled <c>pam</c> in <path>/etc/make.conf</path>.\n"
msgstr ""
"これはデフォルトのセッティングと、ユーザknに対する設定です。\n"
"この制限はsys-apps/shadowパッケージの一部です。\n"
"<path>/etc/make.conf</path>で<c>pam</c>を有効にしている場合、このファイルに制限を設定する必要はありません。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:75
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quotas"
msgstr "Quota"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><impo>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:79
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Make sure the file systems you are working with support quotas. User tools are\n"
"available from <uri link = \"http://www.sf.net/projects/linuxquota/\">the Linux\n"
"DiskQuota project</uri>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:85
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Putting quotas on a file system restricts disk usage on a per-user or per-group\n"
"basis. Quotas are enabled in the kernel and added to a mount point\n"
"in <path>/etc/fstab</path>. The kernel option is enabled in the kernel\n"
"configuration under <c>File systems-&gt;Quota support</c>. Apply the following\n"
"settings, rebuild the kernel and reboot using the new kernel.\n"
msgstr ""
"ファイルシステムにquotaを設定することは、ユーザ毎あるいはグループ毎にディスクの使用を制限することです。\n"
"quotaはkernelで有効にし、<path>/etc/fstab</path>のマウントポイントに設定を追加します。\n"
"kernelの設定でkernelオプションの<c>File systems-&gt;Quota support</c>にある設定を有効にします。\n"
"以下の設定を適用し、kernelをリビルドして、新しいkernelを使ってリブートしてください。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:93
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Start by installing quotas with <c>emerge quota</c>. Then modify your\n"
"<path>/etc/fstab</path> and add <c>usrquota</c> and <c>grpquota</c> to the\n"
"partitions that you want to restrict disk usage on, like in the example below.\n"
msgstr ""
"最初に<c>emerge quota</c>を実行してquotaをインストールします。\n"
"そして、<path>/etc/fstab</path>を編集して以下の例のように、ディスクの使用に制限をかけたいパーティションに<c>usrquota</c>や<c>grpquota</c>を追加します。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:98
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/fstab"
msgstr "/etc/fstab"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:99
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"/dev/sda1 /boot ext2 noauto,noatime 1 1\n"
"/dev/sda2 none swap sw 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda3 / reiserfs notail,noatime 0 0\n"
