"/dev/sda5 /var ext3 noatime,nodev,usrjquota=aquota.user,grpjquota=aquota.group,jqfmt=vfsv1 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda6 /home ext3 noatime,nodev,nosuid,usrjquota=aquota.user,grpjquota=aquota.group,jqfmt=vfsv1 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda7 /usr reiserfs notail,noatime,nodev,ro 0 0\n"
"/dev/cdroms/cdrom0 /mnt/cdrom iso9660 noauto,ro 0 0\n"
"proc /proc proc defaults 0 0\n"
msgstr ""
"/dev/sda1 /boot ext2 noauto,noatime 1 1\n"
"/dev/sda2 none swap sw 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda3 / reiserfs notail,noatime 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda4 /tmp ext3 noatime,nodev,nosuid,noexec,usrquota,grpquota 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda5 /var ext3 noatime,nodev,usrquota,grpquota 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda6 /home ext3 noatime,nodev,nosuid,usrquota,grpquota 0 0\n"
"/dev/sda7 /usr reiserfs notail,noatime,nodev,ro 0 0\n"
"/dev/cdroms/cdrom0 /mnt/cdrom iso9660 noauto,ro 0 0\n"
"proc /proc proc defaults 0 0\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:111
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"On every partition that you have enabled quotas, create the quota files\n"
"(<path>aquota.user</path> and <path>aquota.group</path>) and place them in the\n"
"root of the partition.\n"
msgstr ""
"quotaを有効にしたパーティションすぺてについて、quotaファイル(<path>aquota.user</path>と<path>aquota.group</path>)を作成してください。\n"
"そして、各パーティションのルートに置いてください。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:116
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Creating the quota files"
msgstr "quotaファイルの作成"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:117
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>touch /tmp/aquota.user</i>\n"
"# <i>touch /tmp/aquota.group</i>\n"
"# <i>chmod 600 /tmp/aquota.user</i>\n"
"# <i>chmod 600 /tmp/aquota.group</i>\n"
msgstr ""
"# <i>touch /tmp/aquota.user</i>\n"
"# <i>touch /tmp/aquota.group</i>\n"
"# <i>chmod 600 /tmp/aquota.user</i>\n"
"# <i>chmod 600 /tmp/aquota.group</i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:124
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This step has to be done on every partition where quotas are enabled. After\n"
"adding and configuring the quota files, we need to add the <c>quota</c> script\n"
"to the boot run level.\n"
msgstr ""
"この手順はquotaを有効にした全てのパーティションで行う必要があります。\n"
"quotaの設定を追加した後、<c>quota</c>スクリプトをbootランレベルに加える必要があります。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><impo>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:130
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"XFS does all quota checks internally, and does <e>not</e> need the <c>quota</c>\n"
"script added to the boot runlevel. There may be other filesystems not listed in\n"
"this document with similar behavior, so please read the manpages for your\n"
"filesystem to learn more about how it handles quota checks.\n"
msgstr ""
"XFSは内部的にすべてのquotaをチェックしますので、<c>quota</c>スクリプトをbootランレベルへ追加する必要は<e>ありません。</e>\n"
"このドキュメントで記述されていないファイルシステムで同じような振る舞いをするものがあるかもしれません。\n"
"お使いのファイルシステムでquotaチェックをどのように行うのかより知るためにmanページを読んでください。\n"

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:136
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Adding quota to the boot runlevel"
msgstr "quotaをbootランレベルに追加"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><pre>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:137
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "# <i>rc-update add quota boot</i>\n"
