#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><p>
#: en/security/shb-limits.xml:162
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For more detail read <c>man edquota</c> or the <uri\n"
"link=\"http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/Quota.html\">Quota mini howto</uri>.\n"
